{"id": "art-1179", "label": "Art. 1179", "title": "Art. 1179: Condiţiile esenţiale pentru validitatea contractului", "slug": "art-1179", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 1179: Condi&#355;iile esen&#355;iale pentru validitatea\ncontractului </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'>Condi&#355;iile esen&#355;iale pentru validitatea unui contract sunt:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>1.capacitatea de a contracta;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>2.consim&#355;&#259;mântul\np&#259;r&#355;ilor;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>3.un obiect determinat &#351;i\nlicit;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:18.65pt'><span style='color:black'>4.o cauz&#259; licit&#259;\n&#351;i moral&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)În m&#259;sura în care legea\nprevede o anumit&#259; form&#259; a contractului, aceasta trebuie\nrespectat&#259;, sub sanc&#355;iunea prev&#259;zut&#259; de dispozi&#355;iile\nlegale aplicabile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA 2:Capacitatea\np&#259;r&#355;ilor</span></b></p>"}